The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for image dehazing, which could fall under sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper uses image processing techniques, which could fall under sub-categories such as cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
